{"tid":585383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴工潮】曾嘲葉蔚琳白痴一人罷工 工聯會黎兆聰撞車傷頸","createTime":"2018-03-08T15:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T03:52:34.000Z","uid":22736,"like":198,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"84b062f221f94a0306deb9d5f736afe8861449ea","tid":585383,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180308/57921887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180308%2F57921887&d=NcxA%2FjSO37%2BbTFwcb3mv0J4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3ff0cede\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180308%2F57921887&h=6056a365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180308/57921887</a><br />\n一）「白痴」，搞「一人罷工」。(資料圖片)<br />\n九巴「月薪車長大聯盟」發起人葉蔚琳等人，早前發動罷駛，抗議公司的薪酬調整方案，惟工聯會汽車交通運輸業總工會九巴分會副主任黎兆聰，不點名嘲諷葉「白痴」，只是「一人罷工」。有巴士迷網站引述消息指，黎駕駛的巴士傍晚在彩虹與的士相撞，報稱受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》向警察公共關係科查詢，警方指涉事巴士和的士當時沿清水灣道往彩雲方向行駛，當駛至牛池灣街市對開的燈位時，的士欲向右轉往巴士行駛的行車線，結果撞到巴士。45歲姓黎的巴士司機報稱頸痛，送往聯合醫院。《蘋果》亦致電黎求證，惟當記者表明身份後，對方隨即掛線，亦未有回覆記者的WhatsApp短訊。<br />\n<br />\n「<a href=\"http://hkitalk.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkitalk.net&d=NcxA%2FjSO37%2BbTFwcb3mv0J4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=5401278e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hkitalk.net</a> 香港交通﹒資訊網」facebook專頁轉載WhatsApp群組圖片，並引述消息指，黎駕駛的一輛3M路線九巴，傍晚6點幾在清水灣道牛池灣街市對開與的士相撞，令東九龍一帶交通嚴重擠塞，而黎則報稱受傷送院。專頁「祝願黎車長早日康復！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t【九巴工潮】轟管理層「無腦」 九巴工會：資方睇唔起員工<br />\n即時要聞 12小時前<br />\n\t【九巴工潮】葉蔚琳九巴採上訴機制處理 羅致光稱有需要時會介入<br />\n即時要聞 3小時前<br />\n\t【九巴工潮】龜縮刪片入陸頌雄數 鄧家彪：罷工睇成效唔係睇出鏡<br />\n即時要聞 6小時前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報應得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab111c198f2f63980cdb90b44052a5cbbfc6ab9","tid":585383,"uid":27151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f138f156b81cdb6b8bf9cb672cebda9411555b","tid":585383,"uid":33422,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 站於工人對面"},{"pid":"448cd394cdd9c81fddd9e21e72e99b9ba9c573d8","tid":585383,"uid":84928,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:09:38.000Z","msg":"有冇人發覺呢幾年D報應嚟得好快"},{"pid":"6d0e2edfe9d7800cbc88afa9b0d83aeeaf037fed","tid":585383,"uid":28765,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:11:22.000Z","msg":"一人炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362eb2848c0b70324174378e540fd883247ca491","tid":585383,"uid":1781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5dbb18b6dc71b5576e97a0aa9481b25cbdd9530","tid":585383,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"448cd394cdd9c81fddd9e21e72e99b9ba9c573d8","tid":585383,"uid":84928,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:09:38.000Z","msg":"有冇人發覺呢幾年D報應嚟得好快"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"咁每日都有幾個 窮人跳樓自殺, 算唔算報應??"},{"pid":"3d88d853142399019a46b144f86301f5a7a34ae0","tid":585383,"uid":11001,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:13:36.000Z","msg":"Karma <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b65345b1fdeac5c57b8a25b0d716b21cb69bb6","tid":585383,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T15:15:09.000Z","msg":"白癡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 